Things are moving fast here at the BBQ speakeasy and we’re loving it. 

We’re so excited to bring Texas BBQ as a whole to your doorsteps near or far with bbqdistro.com. 

Thanks to our friends at @lonestarbeer we’ve got plenty of cold beer to get us through this summer!

Whether you’re waiting in line at @zavalasbarbecue , shopping the speakeasy or at one of our speakeasy hangouts, we will have a cold Lone Star ready for you.

Stay tuned as we have some big news coming next month! 

Stock up for this great weather at bbqdistro.com, see you at the shop this week!

Good friend and two-time winner of The Dallas Observer’s “Top 100 Restaurants in Dallas” and Texas Monthly’s “50 Best BBQ Joints 2021”, Zavala’s Barbecue has blown up in the five short years since Joe crafted his unique backyard smoking style, taking over Grand Prairie BBQ where he was born and raised
.
Come enjoy some amazing food and learn a thing or two about Texas BBQ
.
